AskAndWaitCodeBlock, BitkubCodeBlock, BreakCodeBlock, BroadcastAndWaitCodeBlock, BroadcastCodeBlock, ChangeCostumeCodeBlock, ChangeHeightCodeBlock, ChangeSceneCodeBlock, ChangeWidthCodeBlock, HideCodeBlock, HideVarCodeBlock, IfCodeBlock, IfElseCodeBlock, MoveBackwardCodeBlock, MoveForwardCodeBlock, MoveToCodeBlock, RepeatCodeBlock, RotateClockwiseCodeBlock, RotateCounterClockwiseCodeBlock, SayCodeBlock, SetVarCodeBlock, ShowCodeBlock, ShowVarCodeBlock, TransformCodeBlock, WaitCodeBlock, WaitUntilCodeBlock, WhenBitCodeBlock, WhenClickedCodeBlock, WhenKeyPressedCodeBlock, WhenReceivedBroadcastCodeBlock, WhenSceneChangeToCodeBlock, WhenStartCodeBlock, WhileCodeBlock
public abstract class CodeBlock extends javafx.scene.layout.VBox implements Copyable<CodeBlock>, Savable, Executable
A base class for all code blocks. Provide a snapping hint capabilities.

    • mustBeFirstBlock

      public boolean mustBeFirstBlock()
      Whether this code block can only the first block in a code block list. If it is true, it can only be snapped to the top of a code block list and cannot be snap to any other block in a code block list. Returns false by default, subclasses should override to return true when needed.
      Returns:
